Class FactoryBeans

  • com.radiotelescope.controller.spring.FactoryBeans
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FactoryProvider

    public class FactoryBeans
implements FactoryProvider

    Concrete implementation of the interface FactoryProvider interface. It is in charge of making sure the UserWrappers are able to be autowired by Spring when the server is started
